86 (5) Whenever electricity purchased for storage, use, or
87 other consumption is used or consumed by a manufacturer or
88 compounder in an electrolytic or electrothermal manufacturing
89 or compounding process;
90 (6) Whenever natural gas purchased for storage, use, or
91 other consumption is used or consumed by a manufacturer or
92 compounder as a chemical raw material in the manufacturing or
93 compounding of tangible personal property, but not as fuel or
94 energy;
95 (7) Whenever natural gas purchased for storage, use, or
