104 payable by said utility;
105 (9) Whenever electricity purchased for storage, use, or
106 other consumption is used or consumed in a process for the
107 isotopic enrichment of uranium and when said electricity is
108 purchased from a subsidiary corporation of the corporation
109 engaged in the isotopic enrichment of uranium; and
110 (10) Whenever utility services are furnished through
111 the use of a prepaid telephone calling card; and
112 (11)a. Whenever natural gas or electricity purchased
